channel.title: Neo Cerulean - Azure Onyxscore [Dance, Remix, Melodic]
channel.description:
_"ooh look, another Cerulean track from the Auxy 5 hater. what gives, Azure?_
Now calm down for a sec, I've given Auxy 5 a second try after ranting about it non-stop. And now that i've used 5.1, I have to say, boy was I wrong to say that it isn't worth it.
https://soundcloud.com/azureonyx/neo-cerulean
Now I'll be honest, this track is easily better than the other Cerulean tracks I made
I really need to expand on what I can create ___ https://soundcloud.com/azureonyx/neo-cerulean-extended-mix Extended Mix
